Package: psychds
Title: Psych-DS Dataset Creator, Data Dictionary Wizard, and Validator
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Brian", "Leonard", email = "bleonard@mit.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A comprehensive toolkit for creating, editing, and validating
    psychological research datasets following the Psych-DS (Psychological
    Dataset Standard) specification. Provides an interactive 'shiny'
    application for guided dataset creation, tools for generating
    professional data dictionaries, validation against the Psych-DS schema,
    and integration with the Open Science Framework (OSF) for data
    publishing. The Psych-DS standard promotes reproducibility and data
    sharing in psychological science by establishing consistent
    conventions for organizing behavioral and psychological research data.
